{"tid":1206552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅冠聰， 同鄺神， 高下立見","createTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T03:39:32.000Z","uid":258106,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ed3065588a9c92aeebec219042372c9dd0c5ce","tid":1206552,"uid":258106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:34.000Z","msg":"本週，MVP，六月之星，第一個，落嚟，同示威者公開講話嘅立法會，議員，鄺神！<br />\n<br />\n我哋講嘢，一定要用逗號，以表示，對抗鄺神，嘅尊敬。<br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇，真係，成為咗今次，大贏家。民主黨，靠佢，有機會，解決青黃不接，嘅問題，同埋革新。"},{"pid":"51c4ce3ac1abf593c9173cff5e9bf4e6e44fcbd6","tid":1206552,"uid":258106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}